{"tid":1089242,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［樣子巴打大獲］醜化照片發上網 黃曉明夫婦告商家獲賠近10萬","createTime":"2019-04-02T15:45:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-03T05:54:50.000Z","uid":28435,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"52ee071c4a7fbc05014effeccd8ed2f7ad96201b","tid":1089242,"uid":28435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T15:45:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TEqNMCY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTEqNMCY.png&h=4bc57eb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n早前有大陸商家把黃曉明和楊穎（Angelababy）的醜化照片發到網上，藉此宣傳自己的產品，並配文稱「黃曉明半年打一次瘦臉針，如果黃曉明楊穎夫婦都不微整，那麼結婚照應該是這樣的。」對此，他們請律師起訴該商家，指其侵犯了他倆夫妻的名譽權和肖像權。<br />\n<br />\n日前北京法院審判資訊網公佈了審判結果，黃曉明夫婦獲得勝訴，該商家被處罰要連續7日刊登道歉聲明及賠償對方經濟損失80,000元人民幣，精神損害撫慰金5,000元人民幣，共計85,000元人民幣（約99,246港元）。"},{"pid":"2d2fd5a2f3280bf3d1bca588fa12ceb6cfa85379","tid":1089242,"uid":39316,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T15:46:36.000Z","msg":"醜化?<br />\n咁撚樣話自己原本個樣對唔對得住老母呀"},{"pid":"0073ca6d9e70d2ee778681cf3137a19a1d398c37","tid":1089242,"uid":21423,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T15:48:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bf5671a3b074f3759d5e0ce488b52c60f6585d17","tid":1089242,"uid":35014,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T15:59:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f4895504e10387f7f78f8aedf964f38f4aa61dd8","tid":1089242,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T16:04:41.000Z","msg":"樣子巴打好快被引渡返中蟈坐監<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"424eb60a34163450c5c8a9dbbfcdf40cd542884b","tid":1089242,"uid":8410,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T16:07:45.000Z","msg":"講事實都要俾人告？ 仲要賠10 萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90e001a62c50b133a838c3ae288865e86d1f62d9","tid":1089242,"uid":70448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T16:51:53.000Z","msg":